OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1781878275
OL,3,CProposal to cut in fuel duty by 10p to
OL,4,Cease cost of living on island
OL,6,FA Jersey politician has put forward
OL,7,Fthe new States Assembly's first
OL,8,Fproposition, which would remove 10p of
OL,9,Ffuel duty off every litre if approved.
OL,11,FDeputy Lucy Stephenson says the
OL,12,Fproposition would help alleviate cost-
OL,13,Fof-living pressures, which will be
OL,14,Fdebated in the first sitting of the
OL,15,Fnew Assembly in July.
OL,17,FShe told ITV News that she wanted to
OL,18,Fmake the first proposition as a
OL,19,Fpriority and as a promise in her
OL,20,Fmanifesto.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1781878275
OL,3,CProposal to cut in fuel duty by 10p to
OL,4,Cease cost of living on island
OL,6,F"A lot of people are struggling to
OL,7,Fmake ends meet, and the idea is that
OL,8,Fby taking 10p off per litre, that will
OL,9,Fsave five pounds for the average
OL,10,Ffamily car," the politician explains.
OL,12,FThe potential cost of the proposal to
OL,13,Fthe government is unclear, but Deputy
OL,14,FStephenson estimates it would be
OL,15,F#300,000 per month.
OL,17,F"If we're looking at a three-month
OL,18,Ftemporary reduction, then that's just
OL,19,Funder a million pounds.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1781878275
OL,3,CProposal to cut in fuel duty by 10p to
OL,4,Cease cost of living on island
OL,6,F"I would say the government has been
OL,7,Fbringing in more money than it would
OL,8,Fhave forecast because of the rising
OL,9,Fcosts of fuel, because they charge GST
OL,10,Fon fuel."
OL,12,FThe politician's initial proposal is
OL,13,Ffor a reduction between October and
OL,14,FDecember 2026.
OL,16,FHowever, the government could debate
OL,17,Fextending the proposal again at the
OL,18,Fend of the year.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1781878275
OL,3,CProposal to cut in fuel duty by 10p to
OL,4,Cease cost of living on island
OL,6,FShe pointed to unexpectedly high tax
OL,7,Frevenue as a result of higher fuel
OL,8,Fprices.
OL,10,F"We need to see what's happening with
OL,11,Ffuel prices and in a global context,
OL,12,Fwhich is a quickly changing context at
OL,13,Fthe moment," Deputy Stephenson
OL,14,Fexplained.
OL,16,FSome have suggested that the proposal
OL,17,Fruns counter to the government's drive
OL,18,Fto reduce car use and climate change.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1781878275
OL,3,CProposal to cut in fuel duty by 10p to
OL,4,Cease cost of living on island
OL,6,FClimate campaigner Nigel Jones told
OL,7,FITV News that it would "totally ignore
OL,8,Fthe fact that fuel duty was increased
OL,9,Fspecifically to combat climate change.
OL,11,F"This is not a time for backtracking
OL,12,Fon commitments. It's the time for
OL,13,Fdoubling down."
OL,15,FWhen asked by ITV News, Deputy
OL,16,FStephenson denied that the proposal
OL,17,Fruns counter to the government's drive
OL,18,Fto reduce car use.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1781878275
OL,3,CProposal to cut in fuel duty by 10p to
OL,4,Cease cost of living on island
OL,6,F"Realistically, driving is not a
OL,7,Fluxury for people in Jersey; it's not
OL,8,Fa nice-to-have, it's something that
OL,9,Fthey need to do.
OL,11,F"People like carers and those who
OL,12,Fdrive for a living; businesses who
OL,13,Fneed to ferry things around and move
OL,14,Fgoods around, it's an absolute
OL,15,Fnecessity for them."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
